environmentalDataLogging.entities

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.Sample

  • @Entity
public class Sample
extends BaseEntity
    The Sample entity class is the link to the sample table in the EnviroDB database. A Sample represents a result sample the Environmental labs obtains once finished running a experiment
